name: jQuery Notify
tagline: Provides a simple and easy way to insert notification messages using jQuery!
body:
### A simple way to show whats is really happening

jQuery Notify is a [jQuery](http://jquery.com/) plugin that provides a simple and easy way to insert notification messages in your application making it beautiful and cool.

This plugin is under construction. It born to a necessity to display notifications messages. The ideas are not recently and you maybe will find some similar available I’m preparing some new features for jQuery Notify.

### Join us now and share the software

To help us to maintenance jQuery Notify and make its a powerful plugin, make a fork at the GitHub and start to code.

We'll be happy to receive your contributions. So Long, and Thanks for All the Fish.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with jQuery Notify? Check out the [documentation](http://fricardo.com/jquery-notify) or [contact me](http://www.fricardo.com/contato/) and we’ll help you sort it out.
